Interface DirItemInterface

All Known Implementing Classes:
ArchiveCombinedRequest, ArchiveRequest, CombinedRequest, FileCombinedRequest, FileRequest, Request
public interface DirItemInterface

The Request classes returns sortable lists of classes implementing the DirItemInterface to implement directory listings.
